data.description: Lowest-priced home per square foot in the neighborhood and new carpet! Introducing the inviting Shelby design, a two-story residence featuring four bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a 2-car garage. Experience the appeal of stainless-steel kitchen appliances and the enduring charm of granite countertops. Natural light and privacy harmonize gracefully with blinds in every room. The primary bedroom offers a serene escape, complete with a spacious walk-in closet designed for seamless organization.    Outside, discover a comfortably proportioned covered patio that invites relaxation and gatherings. The fully fenced backyard ensures a secure space for leisure and recreation. The entryway extends a warm welcome. This home embodies a well-balanced fusion of contemporary amenities and practicality, crafting an exceptional living environment.
